wednesday the central committee meeting represented a crucial and 
historic moment for the soviet union 
the shaky economy gorbachev inherited when he came to power in 
1985 characterized by a huge budget deficit inflation a 
worthless currency and shortages of consumer goods plunged into 
serious crisis last year 
president gorbachev addressing the central committee on monday 
