pointeapitre wednesday chanting avril murderer get out 
in miami more than 1000 haitians held a candlelight rally on a 
street in the citys little haiti sector seeking pope john paul 
iis support for the overthrow of avril among those in the crowd 
was conservative politician hubert de ronceray who was banished in 
january 
