the associated press of regulations being circulated internally to 
bar anyone under 30 years of age or with less than five years of 
work experience from obtaining official sponsorship to study 
overseas 
other measures have made it more difficult for students to take 
tests for study abroad and to obtain passports without official 
sponsorship 
