the grainy bluegray footage taken during the postmidnight 
attack on dec 20 looks like a fourth of july fireworks display 
with white streams of tracer bullets spraying about and white 
flashes of explosives bursting around the buildings 
rounds from the ac130 gunship carrying out the assault can be 
seen striking roofs and blowing out windows 
fires are visible in several structures after the attack 
the fourengine turboprop ac130 aircraft is armed with three 
kinds of weapons a 105mm howitzer a 40mm bofors cannon and a 
20mm vulcan cannon the tape was made as the plane hovered a few 
hundred feet in the air pouring fire on various targets and snipers 
