we put out a fire that was started by shrapnel 
aouns soldiers did not interfere with civilians leaving 
ashrafiyeh but snipers made targets of roads leading to it and 
other strongholds of geageas militia 
hanan saade a housewife led her three children across leaving 
leaving behind a gutted apartment in ashrafiyeh 
what is left there she said we were all in the shelter 
when it happened shells rained on ashrafiyeh maybe three days 
ago i dont remember the apartment was gone i couldnt even 
find clothes for the children 
