amp cocoa exchange amid mounting supply fears exacerbated by the 
threat of a dockworkers strike next week in brazil the worlds 
largest coffee producer 
on other commodity markets oil futures were mixed precious 
metals advanced grains and soybeans were mostly lower and 
livestock and meat futures were mixed 
